    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>QMU must approve all marketing and publicity materials which utilise the QMU logo. Such materials might include leaflets, posters, advertisements or information to appear on partners’ websites. The reason for this is to allow the University to check the information is accurate and up to date. Similarly, partner institutions may wish to check materials produced by QMU bearing the name or logo of the partner institution.</p>]]></Value>
